            | Hi, I'm a UX/UI Developer currently based in Orlando,FL. What is a 
            | UX/UI Developer you ask? Well, in short, I create the things you see 
            | and interact with on the web. And I make sure you feel good doing it.
            | If you have a web project or just want to chat feel free to contact
            | me below. 
    
